Package nl.naturalis.geneious.csv

Classes and interfaces shared by all operations that import CSV or CSV-like files (including spreadsheets). In other words these classes and interfaces are common to the Sample Sheet Import operation, the CRS import operation and the BOLD import operation.
Author:
Ayco Holleman
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvImportConfig<T extends Enum<T>>
    Contains the user input driving the import of CSV-like files (BOLD Import, CRS Import, Sample Sheet Import).
    CsvImportOptions<T extends Enum<T>,​U extends CsvImportConfig<T>>
    Abstract base class for classes configuring a Geneious dialog that requests user input for the import of CSV-like files.
    CsvImportUtil
    Utility class providing assistence with the import of CSV-like files.
    NoteFactory<T extends Enum<T>>
    Abstract base class for NaturalisNote factories used by the importers of CSV-like files (BOLD Import, CRS Import, Sample Sheet Import).
    Row<T extends Enum<T>>
    Contains the data for a single row within a CSV-like file.
    RowSupplier
    A simple reader for all CSV-like formats suported by the plugin: CSV files, TSV files and spreadsheets.
    SpreadSheetReader
    A simple reader for MS spreadsheets.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidRowException
    Thrown when a row in a CSV-like file contains invalid values.
